                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The target believes a miniature version of their childhood home has built up around them, locking them in place. The target must attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:24] save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected and is temporarily immune to Shackled Memories for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} until the end of their next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is flat-footed and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized} until the end of their next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Restrained]{Restrained} for 1 minute or until they Escape.</p>"
